enhanced_by.reason: Both methods require the conversion of a Date object to a Calendar object, which is a common prerequisite for date comparisons.
The validate method can be used to ensure that the input dates are valid before performing the comparison.
The compareDates method can be invoked before compareYears to ensure that the dates are comparable and to set up the necessary state.
The compareMonths method can be invoked before compareYears to ensure that the months are comparable and to set up the necessary state.
